# Process Call & Local Integration Process

## Project Overview

This SAP CPI project demonstrates how Process Call and Local Integration Process can be used to build modular and reusable integration flows.

The iFlow receives an HTTP request, invokes multiple Local Integration Processes through Process Calls, modifies the message using Content Modifiers, and returns the response to the sender.

---

## Technologies Used

- SAP Integration Suite
- SAP Cloud Integration (CPI)
- HTTP Adapter
- Process Call
- Local Integration Process
- Content Modifier
- Postman

---

## Flow

HTTP Sender
        │
        ▼
Main Integration Process
        │
 ┌───────────────┐
 │ Process Call 1│
 └───────────────┘
        │
 ┌───────────────┐
 │ Process Call 2│
 └───────────────┘
        │
HTTP Response

Each Process Call invokes a Local Integration Process containing Content Modifiers.

